<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Haste effects...<BR>
Flowing Black Silk Sash - 15%<BR>
A Mithril Two-handed Sword - 20%<BR>
Cloak of Flames - 25%<BR>
Runed Bolster Belt - 25%<BR>
Swirlspine Belt - 20%<BR>
Monsoon, Sword of the Swiftwind - 30%<BR>
Ashenwood Spear - 10%<BR>
Executioner's Axe - 10%<BR>
Sunderfury - 35%<BR>
<BR>
These have all been stop watch tested.<BR>
<BR>
Also, on a second note... Sunderfury has the look of a normal<BR>
halberd. Not a bronze axe.</font></td></tr></table>
